doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    link(href='/css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')
    // =====BOX ICONS=====
    link(href='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/boxicons@2.0.5/css/boxicons.min.css', rel='stylesheet')
    title Dennis Kestone
  body
    // ===== HEADER =====
    header.l-header
      nav.nav.bd-grid
        div
          a.nav__logo(href='#') Kestone
        #nav-menu.nav__menu
          ul.nav__list
            li.nav__item
              a.nav__link.active(href='#home') Home
            li.nav__item
              a.nav__link(href='#about') About
            li.nav__item
              a.nav__link(href='#skills') Skills
            li.nav__item
              a.nav__link(href='#work') Work
            li.nav__item
              a.nav__link(href='#contact') Contact
        #nav-toggle.nav__toggle
          i.bx.bx-menu
    main.l-main
      // ===== HOME =====
      section#home.home.bd-grid
        .home__data
          h1.home__title
            | Hi,
            br
            | I am 
            span.home__title-color Kestone
            br
            |  Web Designer 
          a.button(href='#contact') Contact
        .home__social
          a.home__social-icon(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/kestone-dennis-0a777a157/')
            i.bx.bxl-linkedin
          a.home__social-icon(href='https://www.stackoverflow/')
            i.bx.bxl-stack-overflow
          a.home__social-icon(href='https://www.github.com/kes-crypto/')
            i.bx.bxl-github
        .home__img
          img(src='/img/kes.jpg', alt='')
      // ===== ABOUT =====
      section#about.about.section
        h2.section-title About
        .about__container.bd-grid
          .about__img
            img(src='/img/about.jpg', alt='')
          div
            h2.about__subtitle I am Kestone
            p.about__text
              | Hello. I'm an intermediate software developer working with node.js but I started out with front-end as a passion.(I guess you could say, I am a full-stack web-dev!!) 
              br
              | The idea of giving websites a complete and full functionality from the average layout already done by the front-end engineer fascinated me and I had to try it out.
              | (This statement though is neither my take nor is it to be used as any judgemental base for what is or is not a better path in website development.)
              br
              br
              | I started coding in 2017.In 2019, I became serious about it, tirelessly seeking knowledge and I have some projects to show for it. I can now turn your concept into a website with the skills I've learnt over the past year, but there is always more to learn and discover in the software development industry because it is full of untapped knowledge.     
      // ===== SKILLS =====
              
      section#skills.skills.section
        h2.section-title Skills
        .skills__container.bd-grid
          div
            h2.skills__subtitle Profesional Skills
            p.skills__text
              |I work with Vue.js framework for front-end web-development but  I'm also conversant with vanilla javascript.
            .skills__data
              .skills__names
                i.bx.bxl-html5.skills__icon
                span.skills__name HTML5
              .skills__bar.skills__html
              div
                span.skills__percentage 95%
            .skills__data
              .skills__names
                i.bx.bxl-css3.skills__icon
                span.skills__name CSS3
              .skills__bar.skills__css
              div
                span.skills__percentage 65%
            .skills__data
              .skills__names
                i.bx.bxl-javascript.skills__icon
                span.skills__name JAVASCRIPT
              .skills__bar.skills__js
              div
                span.skills__percentage 75%
            .skills__data
              .skills__names
                i.bx.bxl-vuejs.skills__icon
                span.skills__name VUE.JS
              .skills__bar.skills__vue
              div
                span.skills__percentage 50%
            .skills__data
              .skills__names
                i.bx.bxl-nodejs.skills__icon
                span.skills__name NODE.JS
              .skills__bar.skills__node
              div
                span.skills__percentage 60%
                
          div
            img.skills__img(src='/img/work5.jpg', alt='')
      // ===== WORK =====
      section#work.work.section
        h2.section-title Work
        .work__container.bd-grid
          .work__img
            img(src='/img/work1.png', alt='')
          .work__img
            img(src='/img/work2.png', alt='')
          .work__img
            img(src='/img/work3.png', alt='')
          .work__img
            img(src='/img/kes.png', alt='')
          .work__img
            img(src='/img/work5.png', alt='')
          .work__img
            img(src='/img/work6.png', alt='')
      // ===== CONTACT =====
      section#contact.contact.section
        h2.section-title Contact
        .contact__container.bd-grid
          form.contact__form(method='post', action='/index/send')
            input.contact__input(name='name',type='text', id='name', placeholder='Name')
            input.contact__input(name='Email',type='text', placeholder='Email')
            textarea.contact__input(name='message', cols='0', rows='10', placeholder='Tell me something...')
            input.contact__button.button(type='submit', value='Submit' )
    // ===== FOOTER =====
    footer.footer
      p.footer__title KESTONE
      .footer__social
        a.footer__icon(href='https://www.facebook.com/betty.cheruiyot.50/')
          i.bx.bxl-facebook
        a.footer__icon(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/kestone-dennis-0a777a157/')
          i.bx.bxl-linkedin
        a.footer__icon(href='https://www.twitter.com/DeveloperKes')
          i.bx.bxl-twitter
      p Â© 2020 copyright all rights reserved
